,i\}}"></span> as a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_basis=
" title=3D"Standard basis">standard basis</a>. This standard basis makes th=
e complex numbers a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cartesian_plan=
e" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Cartesian plane">Cartesian plane</a>, cal=
