"mw-redirect" title=3D"Commutative algebra (structure)">commutative algebra=
</a> over the reals, and a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Euclide=
an_vector_space" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Euclidean vector space">Euc=
lidean vector space</a> of dimension two.=20
</p>
