</p><p>The addition can be geometrically visualized as follows: the sum of =
two complex numbers <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic=
;">a</span> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b=
</span>, interpreted as points in the complex plane, is the point obtained =
by building a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parallelogram" title=
=3D"Parallelogram">parallelogram</a> from the three vertices <span class=3D=
"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">O</span>, and the points of the=
