ar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">OAB</span> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar=
" style=3D"font-style:italic;">XBA</span> are <a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Congruence_(geometry)" title=3D"Congruence (geometry)">congruen=
t</a>.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Multiplication">Multiplicat=
