c+di)=3Dac-bd+(ad+bc)i.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/4f6f9b21903da13a2ad8a091b391b8ef0d279e0b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.838ex; width:40.812ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle (a=
+bi)\cdot (c+di)=3Dac-bd+(ad+bc)i.}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>For example, <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><s=
pan class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display:=
 none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\dis=
playstyle (2-i)(3+4i)=3D2\cdot 3-((-1)\cdot 4)+(2\cdot 4+(-1)\cdot 3)i=3D10=
+5i.}">
