Alembert">Jean le Rond d'Alembert</a>, states that for any complex numbers =
(called <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient" title=3D"Coef=
ficient">coefficients</a>) <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i><sub>0</sub>,=E2=
=80=89...,=E2=80=89<i>a</i><sub><i>n</i></sub></span>, the equation
