</p><p>The impetus to study complex numbers as a topic in itself first aros=
e in the 16th century when <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algebra=
ic_solution" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Algebraic solution">algebraic s=
