 numbers"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</sp=
an></span></div>
<p>Complex numbers <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i> + <i>bi</i></span> can =
also be represented by <span class=3D"texhtml">2=E2=80=89=C3=97=E2=80=892</=
span> <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matrix_(mathematics)" title=
=3D"Matrix (mathematics)">matrices</a> that have the form
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle {\begin{pmatrix}a&amp;-b\\b&amp;\;\;a\end{pmatrix}}.}">
