l-align: -2.505ex; width:11.178ex; height:6.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle {=
\begin{pmatrix}a&amp;-b\\b&amp;\;\;a\end{pmatrix}}.}"></span>
Here the entries <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=
a</span> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">b</s=
