, brighter spots are farther away from the origin. The color encodes the ar=
gument. The function has zeros for <span class=3D"texhtml">=C2=B11, (2 + <i=
>i</i>)</span> and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pole_(complex_a=
